net.padlocksoftware.padlock.license
Class LicenseIO

java.lang.Object
  net.padlocksoftware.padlock.license.LicenseIO

public final class LicenseIO
extends java.lang.Object

This class provides static methods for license I/O. The LicenseIO class attempts to provide the ultimate flexibility in importing/exporting license instances by offering Input and Output streams as method paramters. The other methods exist for backward compatability.

Author:
Jason Nichols(jason@padlocksoftware.net)

importLicense

public static License importLicense(java.io.File file)
                             throws java.io.IOException,
                                    ImportException
Import a License object from a properly formatted license file. The license may be either signed or unsigned. A successful import doesn't imply the license file is valid, but that the required fields are present. Validation is required to determine license validity.

Parameters:
file - The license file to import
Returns:
The License object stored in the file.
Throws:
java.io.IOException - For any file related exceptions
net.padlocksoftware.license.ImportException - If any required properties are missing or invalid.
